metadata.name: Pepe the Frog on a Rocket
metadata.description:
That's the day Pepe the Frog decided to turn over a new blank white page of his life and set off into space.

The first picture in the series of Pepe's space adventures illustrates the beginning of his star trek across the vast expanse of the universe.

On a rocket to a new planet - let's go!

Picture parameters: 10000 x 7000px
